ğŸ§® Core Mathematical Operations

    Basic Arithmetic: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division, Power, Modulo, Floor Division

    Scientific Functions: Square roots, Exponents, Logarithms (logâ‚â‚€, ln)

    Trigonometry: sin, cos, tan, asin, acos, atan with DEG/RAD support

