    Statistics: Mean, median, mode, standard deviation, variance, range

    Financial Calculations: Future Value (FV), Present Value (PV), Loan Payments (PMT)

ğŸ’¾ Memory & History System

    Memory Functions: Store, recall, add to, subtract from, clear

    Calculation History: Last 100 operations with timestamps

    Persistent Storage: Automatic save/load to JSON file

    Special Variables: ans (last result), mem (memory value), pi, e

